PageNavigatorAgent.response: The Dashboard is the central command center providing comprehensive real-time insights, statistical analysis, and visual representations of all budget transfer activities. It serves executive and departmental managers with critical insights into budget flow patterns, approval bottlenecks, performance metrics, and financial trends through advanced analytics and intuitive visualizations.
